                        <p style="margin-top:0pt; margin-bottom:0pt; text-align:justify; font-size:11pt;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; color:#002060;">KVKK Md. 5/2(&ccedil;): veri sorumlusunun hukuki y&uuml;k&uuml;ml&uuml;l&uuml;ğ&uuml; bendine istinaden</span></p>
